title: Full Show (Durant scores 32 pts in loss to Pelicans, Lakers vs Clippers preview, Dak cleared to play vs Lions)
description:
00:00 Kevin Durant drops 32 pts in Nets 130-108 loss to Pelicans
23:04 Russ scores 19 pts, back in Lakers starting lineup in Lakers loss to Warriors on opening night
1:01:11 Dak is medically cleared to play vs Detroit
1:11:42 Kawhi's Clippers face LeBron's Lakers tonight
1:20:42 Travis Kelce wants Chiefs to sign OBJ
1:31:25 20th anniversary of Shannon recording the most receiving yards by a TE in a single game with 214
1:42:02 Cowboys players reportedly told Sirianni he doesn't belong on same field last season
1:49:31 Luka Doncic scores 35 pts in Mavs 107-105 loss to Suns
1:54:46 Giannis' Bucks face Embiid's Sixers tonight
